304
00:21:16,279 --> 00:21:17,200
Holy fuck.

305
00:21:18,039 --> 00:21:18,880
It's strong.

306
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,480
Do you like sushi?

307
00:22:03,279 --> 00:22:04,400
I'm not hungry.

308
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,759
No.

309
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:10,200
