409
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,319
How's it going?

410
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:04,799
Fine.

411
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:05,839
Yeah?

412
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,279
Later.

413
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:26,039
See?

414
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:30,680
Told you, kiddo. Everyone has a price.
Some are cheaper than others.

415
00:29:30,759 --> 00:29:33,160
I'll get the hard drive tonight.

416
00:29:33,640 --> 00:29:35,599
You don't even know the guy.

417
00:29:36,039 --> 00:29:38,359
That's why I'm meeting him at the club.

418
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,599
The blackout party.

419
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,799
You can do anything in the dark.

420
00:29:42,119 --> 00:29:42,960
Anything?

421
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:46,039
-Except crochet.
-I'm going with you, just in case.

422
00:29:46,119 --> 00:29:47,319
OK, Dad.

423
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:50,880
Rebe, what would you do if you knew 
Samu was cheating on you?

424
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:53,480
-What?
-Where'd that come from?

425
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,440
