with nothing.

492
00:34:10,599 --> 00:34:12,559
Think about your future, honey.

493
00:34:16,039 --> 00:34:17,960
About our future.

494
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:27,320
You're crazy, Valerio!

495
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:29,000
